elops her newly discovered abilities with the guidance of Luke Skywalker, who is unsettled by the strength of her powers. Meanwhile, the Resistance prepares to do battle with the First Order.','2017-12-13','2018-03-28','/kOVEVeg59E0wsnXmF9nrh6OmWII.jpg','/5Iw7zQTHVRBOYpA0V6z0yypOPZh.jpg',4,152,10,'star-wars-the-last-jedi'),(181812,'tt2527338','Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker','Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker','The saga will end. The story lives forever.','The surviving Resistance faces the First Order once again as the journey of Rey, Finn and Poe Dameron continues. With the power and knowledge of generations behind them, the final battle begins.','2019-12-18','2020-04-04','/db32LaOibwEliAmSL2jjDF6oDdj.jpg','/auJKGst3vXpJozHZh4nMFs0xWIU.jpg',4,142,10,'star-wars-the-rise-of-skywalker'),(238636,'tt2975578','The Purge: Anarchy','The Purge: Anarchy','','One night per year, the government sanctions a 12-hour period in which citizens can commit any crime they wish -- including murder -- without fear of punishment or imprisonment. Leo, a sergeant who lost his son, plans a vigilante mission of revenge during the mayhem. However, instead of a death-dealing avenger, he becomes the unexpected protector of four innocent strangers who desperately need his help if they are to survive the night.','2014-07-18','2014-10-22','/qwqHHZLZSUvMkAMQ47ymtfjEifY.jpg','/blfZnm6StMPnTY35kaooPBCsSVp.jpg',5,103,256322,'the-purge-anarchy'),(260346,'tt2446042','Taken 3','Taken 3','It ends here','Ex-government operative Bryan Mills finds his life is shattered when he\'s falsely accused of a murder that hits close to home. As he\'s pursued by a savvy police inspector, Mills employs his particular set of skills to track the real killer and exact his unique brand of justice.','2014-12-16','2025-05-06','/vzvMXMypMq7ieDofKThsxjHj9hn.jpg','/vFm4pF0BgaWPj0i2zEiZO6TqEQ0.jpg',4,109,135483,'taken-3'),(267860,'tt3300542','London Has Fallen','London Has Fallen','The world\'s leaders have assembled. So have their enemies.','In London for the Prime Minister\'s funeral, Mike Banning discovers a plot to assassinate all the attending world leaders.','2016-03-04','2016-06-20','/iEbLkYzyiUdOKNK4WNBFyGH7r2Y.jpg','/gYQ30Jer6qMZSKxeDmcibueeq0T.jpg',5,99,386534,'london-has-fallen'),(273481,'tt3397884','Sicario','Sicario','The border is just another line to cross.','An idealistic FBI agent is enlisted by a government task force to aid in the escalating war against drugs at the border area between the U.S. and Mexico.','2015-09-17','2016-02-14','/lz8vNyXeidqqOdJW9ZjnDAMb5Vr.jpg','/fKPgObonYgPgCdu88yjV7Hpn7Dp.jpg',5,122,496796,'sicario'),(284536,'tt2039393','The Gambler','The Gambler','The only way out is all in','Literature professor Jim Bennett leads a secret life as a high-stakes gambler. Always a risk-taker, Bennett bets it all when he borrows from a gangster and offers his own life as collateral. Staying one step ahead, he pits his creditor against the operator of an illicit gambling ring while garnering the attention of Frank, a paternalistic loan shark. As his relationship with a student deepens, Bennett must risk everything for a second chance.','2014-12-25','2025-06-03','/hIgU3cxn7Y87joQGM3srofnXOm5.jpg','/yNz3HMbPDIawT7WH0MzkTrBBa1w.jpg',5,111,NULL,'the-gambler'),(316727,'tt4094724','The Purge: Election Year','The Purge: Election Year','Keep America great','Two years after choosing not to kill the man who killed his son, former police sergeant Leo Barnes has become head of security for Senator Charlene Roan, the front runner in the next Presidential election due to her vow to eliminate the Purge. On the night of what should be the final Purge, a betrayal from within the government forces Barnes and Roan out onto the street where they must fight to survive the night.','2016-07-01','2016-10-07','/gg7tlp45xqGWMra0sqQVPvybje2.jpg','/a7V3ZXCDAk3P7GjpgfN0IInjh0r.jpg',5,109,256322,'the-purge-election-year'),(324668,'tt4196776','Jason Bourne','Jason Bourne','You know his name','Th